Package main.modeinfo

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ModeInfo
    An Interface to pass the current state of the program to the Formatter.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EditModeInfo
    The ModeInfo that is passed when the user is in the EditMode.
    EmptyModeInfo
    A ModeInfo that is used when the user is in the normal mode, without any specific mode to print out.
    SearchModeInfo
    The ModeInfo for the state when the program is in the search mode.

    Enum Description
    ModeInfo.Type
